        "id": "C0024",
        "name": "SolarWinds Compromise",
        "description": "<p>During the <a href=\"https://attack.mitre.org/campaigns/C0024\">SolarWinds Compromise</a>, <a href=\"/groups/G0016\">APT29</a> obtained a list of users and their roles from an Exchange server using <code>Get-ManagementRoleAssignment</code>.</p>",
